data.description: LOAN AMOUNT OF $218,000 IS ASSUMABLE @ 2.99%. Welcome to the epitome of modern living in the charming Roffee plan, a pristine residence located in a picturesque gated community. This meticulously designed home offers an inviting open-concept living space, featuring 3 bedrooms and 2 baths that blend seamlessly for a harmonious living experience.  As you step through the entrance, a lovely foyer sets the tone, creating a warm welcome for both homeowners and guests alike. The heart of this home lies in its main living area, where the spacious family room seamlessly connects to the gorgeous kitchen. The kitchen, adorned with beautiful granite countertops, is not only a culinary haven but also an aesthetic delight.  The master suite, strategically placed for optimum privacy, becomes a sanctuary within the home. Boasting a spacious master bath and a massive walk-in closet, it provides the perfect retreat at the end of a long day. This residence also embraces the convenience of home automation, ensuring a seamless and modern lifestyle.  Step outside onto the covered patio, an ideal space for al fresco dining or relaxing with a good book. The two-car garage adds practicality to this charming abode, completing the perfect picture of a home designed for both style and functionality.  What sets this property apart is its 'like-new' condition, as it has barely been lived in. This unique feature positions the home as an exceptional opportunity for those seeking a turnkey residence.  The community itself is a hidden gem, offering an array of amenities for residents to enjoy. From a sparkling pool to a playground and scenic jogging trails, there's something for everyone. This property is not just a home; it's a lifestyle waiting to be embraced. Don't miss the chance to make this beautiful haven your own - schedule a viewing today, as opportunities like these seldom last long in the market.
